The IMI Max patches is a collection of Max patches made or used at the design for interaction and moving image course at the London College of Communication (University of the Arts London). 

This light version comes without the applications, externals, help, java-classes, jsextension and media folders. To install, you can either launch the install.command (Max 6 or 6.1) or manually drop the IMIpatches folder in the packages folder (Max 6.1 and above).


If you have any questions, please e-mail : n.marechal@lcc.arts.ac.uk
